title: The Lengths We Go To | Flashbomb E5 Flash Lining
description:
Rip Curl's new and exclusive E5 Flash Lining with 25% more stretch, faster drying time and a lighter lower profile.

Paired with slimline liquid tape technology and E5 stress point taping for the ultimate in sealed seams, this is the best cold water wetsuit ever made.

Music: Conway Hambone
Track: Cuban Stomp
Source: Getty Images

transcripts: The quest is always to make the ultimate cold wear performance wetsuit, to keep brief with the E5 flash lining  is to take out a little flash lining and make it as stretchy as any other material we have, quick drying, and warmth and high stretch all together in one, you  basically have E5. And the new E5 material was incredible we'll start flexible and just easy to get on and off and held the warmth for us with the flexibility too just made it easy to travel around inside warm and yeah I'm siked on it.
